      <title>Sycamore Partners 探索对服装制造商 Gildan Activewear 的竞购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/clothing-maker-gildan-says-it-s-evaluating-potential-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，私募股权公司 Sycamore Partners 正在探索对 Gildan Activewear Inc. 提出收购要约，该公司是一家拥有 American Apparel 品牌的加拿大服装制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/clothing-maker-gildan-says-it-s-evaluating-potential-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
